<h1><span>Hi, I'm Nico!</span></h1>
<p>
    Welcome to my website. I write about computing, history, and philosophy. My technical interests span machine learning, multi-agent systems, and performance-oriented backends. I work with <span style="color: #3776ab">Python</span>, <span style="color: #00add8">Go</span>, <span style="color: #ce422b">Rust</span>, <span style="color: #5967d8">C</span>, and <span style="color: #3178c6">TypeScript</span>. I enjoy building things that need to be fast and scale well.
</p>

<h2>Writing</h2>
<p>
    I avoid being prescriptive and instead prefer to frame my experiences and how I've learned or grown from them. I <a href="/writing">write about</a> programming, statistics, psychology, philosophy, and history.
</p>
<p>
    Writing helps me think. I welcome critiques, fact checking, and fresh angles I didn't consider. Reach me at {% include "email.njk" %}!
</p>

<h2>Studies</h2>
<p>
